{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/Wishlist.png?t=1734736693\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/tactical-card.png?t=1734736693\" />Dire Fog combines the best strategic elements of turn based tactical combat and deck building card games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct your deck and then play it out on a grid, strategically maneuvering your minions and spells into position to outwit your opponent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/Britonia_Smoke_610_NARROW.jpg?t=1734736693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/no-randomness.png?t=1734736693\" />Choose the order your cards are drawn in when you build your deck. There are no random effects in the game and no shuffling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can only win through thoughtful deck construction and outplaying your opponent in game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/strategic.png?t=1734736693\" />Dire Fog is designed to be first and foremost a strategic PVP experience. You will build a deck and play it against an opponent selected based on your skill level online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/+300Cards.png?t=1734736693\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unique effects that play into positioning mechanics and offer opportunities to set up and outplay your opponent</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Stunning visual effects, hand drawn illustrations, and voice overs that will leave you breathless</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Lore and world building baked into every card that will draw you in to the world of Dire Fog</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/community.png?t=1734736693\" />Dire Fog is currently in the closed alpha stage of development. We are welcome dedicated fans of CCGs and deep tactical combat games to join our community and provide their feedback and thoughts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our discord server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/extras/Discord.png?t=1734736693\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734736693","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734736693","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/b6f11ec2fa029aaa5b7ac75efcdfe89fdbf9fe9d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734736693","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888910/b6f11ec2fa029aaa5b7ac75efcdfe89fdbf9fe9d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734736693","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":"This is a card game and a small number of cards have images that depict gritty cartoon/illustrated violence. There are also a small number of